# Click Trainer v2.7
A rewritten version of [d0sboots' click trainer](https://github.com/d0sboots/PerfectTower/blob/main/README.md#button-coordinate-finder).

It can auto seperate the tall screen data and wide screen data, making it less likely to mess up and insert a wrong datapoint.

Also uses a different way to process data, which is slower but allows more accurate formula under some cases.

Check the above link for how to use the script(too lazy to write one).

## Modes
Edit the mode on the first line of the `main` script
- `simple`: Produces regular data that works for all resolutionand constant ui size, faster.
- `manual`: Produces more data that works for different ui sizes, slower.
